repair_recipe.description: A fiery splinter from a <GlobalColor.Attention>spicy</> candy.

GreatAxeMint.description: A menacing greataxe made of <GlobalColor.Attention>minty candy</> that gives your enemies a chill.

hidden_status_effects.description: The final hit in your 3 hit combo increases your attack speed for a short duration.

repair_recipe.description: A nugget of breath-freshening mint. Much more filling at this size.

PickAxeSalty.description: The epic powers of sodium ions create the perfect mining tool. Busting objects with the same intensity as <GlobalColor.Attention>salt</> busts blandness.

hidden_status_effects.description: The final hit in your 3 hit combo applies bleed to the target.

repair_recipe.description: A clean piece of <GlobalColor.Attention>salt</> that's surprisingly sharp. Shouldn't be eaten by itself, but it's a great flavor enhancement ingredient in meals.

BossKeyAntQueenRedKill.description: The <GlobalColor.Attention>red ant queen</>'s favorite food, but laced with deadly poison.

BossKeyAntQueenRedInfect.description: A mold-infested preparation of the <GlobalColor.Attention>red ant queen</>'s favorite food.

BossKeyAntQueenBlackKill.description: The <GlobalColor.Attention>black ant queen</>'s favorite food, but laced with deadly poison.

BossKeyAntQueenBlackInfect.description: A mold-infested preparation of the <GlobalColor.Attention>black ant queen</>'s favorite food.

BossKeyAntQueenFireKill.description: The <GlobalColor.Attention>fire ant queen</>'s favorite food, but laced with deadly poison.

BossKeyAntQueenFireInfect.description: A mold-infested preparation of the <GlobalColor.Attention>fire ant queen</>'s favorite food.

ShieldAntInfected.description: A grotesque shield crafted from the ever-glowing parts of <GlobalColor.Attention>infected ants</>.

main_status_effects.description: Increases your resistance to taking damage.
Shields prioritize defense over offense, raising block strength but lowering damage dealt.

repair_recipe.description: An unidentifiable chunk of an <GlobalColor.Attention>infected ant</>.

UniqueSpatula.description: The tried and true, perfectly seasoned spatula of your robotic friend. Can still flip a mean patty.

main_status_effects.description: Refills a bit of hunger every time you defeat an enemy.

repair_recipe.description: This stuff sticks to anything! Can repair armor and weapons that have been upgraded past a certain point.

AntQueenScepter.description: A quick attacking sign of royalty, perfect for summoning a horde to your side.

main_status_effects.description: Increases the HP of all creatures summoned by you.

hidden_status_effects.description: Your attacks are faster.

repair_recipe.description: Sturdy chunks of <GlobalColor.Attention>red ant</> that seem useful in a variety of crafts.

ArrowLips.description: An arrow that carries the spirit of love, occasionally forcing your target to fight alongside you.

BombStickyTier3.description: A bomb of the highest caliber, designed for death.

SpearInfectedAnt.description: A grotesque spear of pure pulsating destruction. Crafted from various foul parts and mandibles of <GlobalColor.Attention>infected ants</>.

main_status_effects.description: Your charge attacks cause explosive aftershocks.

hidden_status_effects.description: The final hit in your 3 hit combo does more damage.

repair_recipe.description: The devastating mandibles of an <GlobalColor.Attention>infected ant</>.
Crusty fuzz from fiber-dwelling <GlobalColor.Attention>dust mites</>.

repair_recipe.description: A non-Newtonian sludge found in average foes that becomes crystalized the more it's kneaded and slapped together into a larger volume.
